        {
            "title": "西門子據悉考慮剝離西門子醫療股份",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"西門子據悉考慮剝離西門子醫療股份\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Qe5SSTjVewFeCz0Kpay4Gg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-10/c2ad4050-9f8b-11f0-9dd5-0cf4ad2bcc9c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">西門子據悉考慮剝離西門子醫療股份</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%A5%BF%E9%96%80%E5%AD%90%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%89%9D%E9%9B%A2%E8%A5%BF%E9%96%80%E5%AD%90%E9%86%AB%E7%99%82%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%BD-171320294.html",
